		/// <para>Each resultset row returns a component that controls (reduces) log generation rate in a Hyperscale database. There are multiple <a href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/hyperscale-architecture'>components in Hyperscale tier architecture</a> that could contribute to the reducing log generation rate.<br/>
